      "acceptanceCriteria": "CFD solver must have documented V&V test suite with version-controlled release notes and issue tracking.",
      "rationale": "ANSYS Fluent 2023 R1 was used under a controlled software environment. The solver vendor provides a published V&V test suite (ANSYS Fluent Verification Manual 2023). Version control and change logs were reviewed; no open critical defects affecting rotating-frame hemolysis simulations were identified. SQA level 2 requirements are satisfied."
    },
    {
