      "factorType": "Numerical code verification",
      "type": "CredibilityFactor",
      "requiredLevel": 2,
      "achievedLevel": 2,
      "factorStatus": "assessed",
      "acceptanceCriteria": "Solver must pass at least two canonical benchmark problems relevant to rotating turbomachinery flows.",
      "rationale": "Fluent 2023 R1 was verified against the Taylor-Couette flow benchmark and the FDA nozzle benchmark (ASME V&V 40 Annex B). Both benchmarks produced results within stated solver tolerances. Code verification at gradation 2 is confirmed."
    },
    {
      "factorStandard": "ASME-VV40-2018",
      "factorType": "Discretization error",
      "type": "CredibilityFactor",
      "requiredLevel": 2,
      "achievedLevel": 2,
      "factorStatus": "assessed",
      "acceptanceCriteria": "GCI for primary QoI (RH index) must be below 5 % on the production mesh.",
      "rationale": "Grid Convergence Index analysis on three systematically refined meshes yielded GCI = 1.7 % for RH at the worst-case operating point (3500 RPM, 2 L/min). The production mesh (11.6 M elements) is confirmed mesh-independent. Discretisation error level 2 is achieved."
    },
    {
      "factorStandard": "ASME-VV40-2018",
      "factorType": "Test conditions",
      "type": "CredibilityFactor",
      "requiredLevel": 2,
      "achievedLevel": 2,
      "factorStatus": "assessed",
      "acceptanceCriteria": "Experimental boundary conditions must be measured and reported with stated uncertainty; CFD boundary conditions must match within measurement uncertainty.",
      "rationale": "PIV experiments were conducted in a closed-loop test rig with calibrated Coriolis flow meters (±0.5 % FS) and optical tachometers (±1 RPM). Fluid temperature was controlled to 37 ± 0.5 °C. CFD boundary conditions were set to measured mean values; deviations were within measurement uncertainty for all five operating points."
    },
    {
      "factorStandard": "ASME-VV40-2018",
      "factorType": "Output comparison",
      "type": "CredibilityFactor",
      "requiredLevel": 2,
      "achievedLevel": 2,
      "factorStatus": "assessed",
      "acceptanceCriteria": "Normalised RMS velocity error < 10 % and RH index mean absolute relative error < 10 % across all operating points.",
      "rationale": "Velocity field nRMSE was 6.8 % (PIV vs CFD, averaged across five planes and five operating points). RH index mean absolute relative error was 4.3 % across five operating points. Both acceptance criteria are satisfied at gradation 2."
    },
    {
