      "factorStatus": "assessed",
      "acceptanceCriteria": "Solver residuals must converge to at least 1e-5 for all transport equations; mass imbalance must be below 0.01 %.",
      "rationale": "All simulations were run to convergence with residuals below 1e-6 for continuity, momentum, and turbulence equations. Mass imbalance across the impeller domain was below 0.005 %. Numerical solver error is controlled at gradation 1."
    },
