      "acceptanceCriteria": "Simulation setup must be reviewed by an independent analyst; checklist-based review documented.",
      "rationale": "An independent CFD analyst reviewed the simulation setup against a 42-item checklist covering geometry import, mesh topology, boundary condition assignment, turbulence model selection, and post-processing scripts. No critical errors were identified. Use error controlled at gradation 1."
