      "type": "CredibilityFactor",
      "requiredLevel": 2,
      "achievedLevel": 2,
      "factorStatus": "assessed",
      "acceptanceCriteria": "Turbulence model selection must be justified by published benchmark data for rotating pump flows; hemolysis model must be peer-reviewed.",
      "rationale": "The SST k-omega turbulence model was selected based on its demonstrated performance in FDA pump benchmark studies (Stewart et al. 2012, Hariharan et al. 2011). The Giersiepen hemolysis power-law model is peer-reviewed and widely adopted in regulatory CFD submissions. Model form uncertainty at gradation 2 is accepted."
    },
