      "acceptanceCriteria": "All material properties and boundary condition inputs must be sourced from calibrated measurements or published literature with stated uncertainty.",
      "rationale": "Blood analogue viscosity was measured with a cone-and-plate rheometer (±2 %). Pump geometry was digitised from CMM measurements of the physical impeller (±0.02 mm). Inlet velocity profiles were derived from PIV measurements. All inputs are traceable to calibrated sources with documented uncertainty. Model inputs at gradation 2 are confirmed."
    },
