      "rationale": "Test samples factor is not assessed at MRL 2 for this COU. Validation relies on PIV velocity measurements and in-vitro hemolysis index data from a single pump unit representative of the design intent. Sample-to-sample variability assessment is outside the scope of MRL 2 requirements."
