    "role": "Credibility assessment team",
    "outcome": "Accepted",
    "rationale": "All seven assessed credibility factors meet or exceed their required gradation levels at MRL 2. Six factors are appropriately scoped out or not assessed at MRL 2. Validation evidence from PIV and in-vitro hemolysis experiments demonstrates that the CFD model reliably predicts worst-case hemolysis operating conditions for the FDA generic centrifugal blood pump under CPB conditions. The UQ campaign results (summarised in TR-2024-CPB-07) confirm that the RH < 1 acceptance criterion is robust to realistic input variability. The model is accepted for the stated COU.",
